{"tid":499803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫友人裝修無糧出　裝修工人揮鎅刀攀窗尋死","createTime":"2017-12-15T08:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T10:30:05.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"99c4218a4d32c498770dd2409775e5e5190acc7d","tid":499803,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171215/photo/bkn-20171215104910759-1215_00822_001_01p.jpg?20171215155437\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171215%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171215104910759-1215_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20171215155437&h=0c008df7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">持刀男子走到窗邊大叫。（曾志恒攝）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171215/photo/bkn-20171215104910759-1215_00822_001_02b.jpg?20171215155437\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171215%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171215104910759-1215_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20171215155437&h=b8fa717a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">飛將軍游繩戒備。（曾志恒攝）</span><br />\n<br />\n裝修工人揮鎅刀攀窗尋死。早上10時許， 身穿紅衣的姓蕭（50歲）男子，與人傾電話後情緒激動，反鎖在牛池灣坪石邨黃石樓一單位企圖自殺，其姓張（31歲）男同事得悉後報案。警方及消防接報到場，紅衣男拒絕開門，右手持鎅刀在窗邊揮舞，一度以鎅刀架頸，又將其中一隻腳踏出窗台大叫大嚷，險象環生。消防擔心他跳樓尋死，在樓下張開救生氣墊，並派出2名「飛將軍」在樓上單位的外牆游繩戒備。警方又將大廈其中一個出入口封鎖。<br />\n<br />\n期間，警方派出談判專家到場游說，又大打溫情牌，向紅衣男說：「你都有家人㗎？你太太等緊你㗎，你開門啦！」紅衣男聞言態度軟化，自行開門讓救援人員入屋，而2名「飛將軍」亦由涉事單位入屋，事件在對峙3小時後終告結束。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息稱，蕭為裝修工人，在上址替友人裝修，疑因有人拖欠裝修費用，他一時情緒激動尋死。他事後被送上救護車送院檢查時稱：「無良業主唔畀錢，大家係朋友，呃咗我哋幾萬蚊」。警方經初步調查後，得悉他受金錢問題困擾，現場未有檢獲遺書，相信事件無可疑，案件列作企圖自殺。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171215/bkn-20171215104910759-1215_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171215%2Fbkn-20171215104910759-1215_00822_001.html&d=oWaruqJxbgGKsQHa%2FbqJqTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=8650cd90\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171215/bkn-20171215104910759-1215_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"423990c1de411c40dec534842998a4ff2a6a3ded","tid":499803,"uid":19552,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:15:39.000Z","msg":"點解係自殺唔係去同報仇先"},{"pid":"36f3ed9dbefbd7c3f2b71c03942427c85032f7a9","tid":499803,"uid":81197,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:17:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解係自殺唔係去同報仇先</blockquote><br />\n係人地屋企自殺 變凶宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b056a4c5a85c2f0226f81610c25d3223c548cb1","tid":499803,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:18:43.000Z","msg":"人地錯，但自己尋死？<br />\n<br />\n心理要點扭曲先做得出"},{"pid":"68bf428442086e1535abec51b37a87c2c44dacb6","tid":499803,"uid":2772,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:20:02.000Z","msg":"冇撚用<br />\n錢又收唔到<br />\n樓又跳唔成"},{"pid":"8c443fd2773f175839a55eaf6c113aa06ed4c0fa","tid":499803,"uid":84928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:26:47.000Z","msg":"有膽自殺，點解唔去隊死個陷家鏟先"},{"pid":"f3e18f6d324c93157c8872b8ff2f32408508efa6","tid":499803,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:46:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地錯，但自己尋死？<br />\n<br />\n心理要點扭曲先做得出</blockquote><br />\n夠撚膽先算"},{"pid":"69e52412c64adb5522207d8bc8748963d7a75274","tid":499803,"uid":21222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:49:56.000Z","msg":"裝修走數聽得多，要自殺式追數第一次聽"},{"pid":"db8371d74cb0a72cc4ffd45161fa6b49744cde2c","tid":499803,"uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T08:50:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解係自殺唔係去同報仇先</blockquote><br />\n係人地屋企自殺 變凶宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔比幾皮換黎唔見一球"},{"pid":"ec1d2024b61781ad6a8015878164a96a5471da8b","tid":499803,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTim